r nationwide expansion by  as part of the initiative it is entering new markets as well as returning to markets where it had a presence in past years in support of this objective the chain began airing ads in states several hundred miles from the nearest location this is similar to a strategy used for years by sonic drivein in its national expansion efforts this jack in the box off us highway  is one of five company outlets in laredo texas notice the s logo the expansion strategy at that time was targeted at colorado delaware florida and texas in  the first new colorado store opened in golden marking an end to jack in the boxs yearlong absence from the state in albuquerque new mexico several locations opened in june  jack in the box restaurants last made an appearance in the albuquerque market approximately two decades ago in september  it was announced that  underperforming companyowned jack in the box restaurants located mostly in texas and the southeast would close in march  jack in the box launched the munchie mobile in san diego a food truck that will serve jacks burgers and fries in june  jack in the box launched their second food truck in the southeast region of the united statescitation needed another truck was launched for the northern texas area in april  in january  jack in the box opened its first of three locations in the indianapolis area a few months later the first ohio location opened in september  in west chester restatementedit on december   the company restated three years of results due to an accounting change that prompted the company to cut firstquarter and  earnings expectations see alsoedit list of hamburger restaurants companies portal food portal san diego portal referencesedit  jack in the box inc new  q quarterly report form q xbrl united states securities and exchange commission february     jack in the box inc new  annual report form k xbrl united states securities and exchange commission november     jack in the box inc aboutus retrie