to have way too much fun along the way what we offer the cherry on top working with us fun is our middle name restaurant careers jobs hot off the grill featured jobs home working with us what we offer news  events job search scroll to top jack in the box inc  corporate responsibility facebook twitter youtube contact us community jack in the box is dedicated to making a positive difference in the communities in which our employees franchisees and guests work and live  one way that we give back is through the jack in the box foundation established in  the jack in the box foundation is a c  nonprofit organization that primarily supports causes that help atrisk children and youth some of our primary community partners are share our strength’s no kid hungry campaign is ending child hunger in america by ensuring all children get the healthy food they need every day the jack in the box foundation donates to the preuss school to help provide transportation and scholarships to lowincome students who strive to become the first in their families to graduate from college the jack in the box foundation teams up with our employees and franchisees to help children being cared for by children’s hospitals  our contributions help children’s hospitals offer families the promise of a healthier future the jack in the box foundation helped big brothers big sisters launch operation bigs which provides mentors to children from military families the jack in the box foundation teams up with our employees franchisees and guests to raise money for march of dimes’ annual walk our donations help improve the health of babies by preventing birth defects premature birth and infant mortality the jack in the box foundation sponsors every monday matters which inspires youth to understand how much they matter and empowers them to make a difference jack in the box employees teamed up with every monday matters to install handpainted tiles at monarch school which serves youth impacted by homelessness monarch school is another community partner of the jack in the box foundation additionally the company encourages employees to volunteer in our corporate and restaurant communities and provides them with opportunities to participate in group efforts through our brand ambassadors program brand ambassadors are employees who give back to the community by volunteering for activities ranging from serving meals to seniors to refurbishing homes for disabled veterans click below to learn more about some of our amazing community partners